<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ninja Executor - 官方首页</title>
    <style>
        *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;}
        body{
            background:#0b0b13;
            color:#fff;
            min-height:100vh;
            text-align:center;
            padding-top:80px;
        }
        .logo{font-size:50px;font-weight:bold;color:#7b2cbf;margin-bottom:20px;}
        .desc{color:#aaa;font-size:18px;margin-bottom:50px;}
        .btn{
            display:inline-block;
            padding:16px 40px;
            margin:12px;
            background:#7b2cbf;
            color:#fff;
            text-decoration:none;
            border-radius:8px;
            font-weight:bold;
            transition:0.3s;
        }
        .btn:hover{background:#9d4edd;transform:scale(1.05);}
        .btn2{background:#222;border:1px solid #7b2cbf;}
        .btn2:hover{background:#111;}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="logo">NINJA EXECUTOR</div>
    <div class="desc">免费 Roblox 电脑端执行器 | 需要密钥才能使用</div>

    <a href="key.html" class="btn">🔑 获取密钥</a>
    <a href="executor.html" class="btn btn2">💻 打开执行器</a>
</body>
</html>

